OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779369077
OL,3,CMan arrested following investigation
OL,4,Cinto 25-tonne illegal waste dump in
OL,5,CWigan
OL,7,FA man has been arrested as part of an
OL,8,Fongoing investigation into large-
OL,9,Fscale, illegal dumping of waste at
OL,10,Fmultiple sites across England,
OL,11,Fincluding at Bolton House Road in
OL,12,FWigan.
OL,14,FOfficers from West Midlands Police
OL,15,Farrested a 58-year-old male from the
OL,16,FBirmingham area on suspicion of
OL,17,Fenvironmental, fraud and money
OL,18,Flaundering offences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
