FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779369077
OL,3,CMan arrested following investigation
OL,4,Cinto 25-tonne illegal waste dump in
OL,5,CWigan
OL,7,FThe suspect has now been released on
OL,8,Fconditional bail pending further
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FThe 25,000 tonne fly-tipping site has
OL,12,Fleft some local residents coping with
OL,13,Finfestations of rats and flies.
OL,15,FDescribed as one of the largest in the
OL,16,Fcountry, the mountain of illegally fly-
OL,17,Ftipped waste, which is on a two acre
OL,18,Fsite in Wigan, sits next to houses, a
OL,19,Fplaying field and a primary school.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779369077
OL,3,CMan arrested following investigation
OL,4,Cinto 25-tonne illegal waste dump in
OL,5,CWigan
OL,7,FIt is believed the waste is partly on
OL,8,Fland owned by the Duchy of Lancaster,
OL,9,Fthe King's private estate, who say
OL,10,Fthey are working with Wigan Council
OL,11,Fand other agencies to sort the problem
OL,12,Fout.
OL,14,FThe Environment Agency's investigation
OL,15,Fis being led by its National
OL,16,FEnvironmental Crime Unit, which says
OL,17,Fit is seeking to track down those
OL,18,Finvolved and hold them accountable.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779369077
OL,3,CMan arrested following investigation
OL,4,Cinto 25-tonne illegal waste dump in
OL,5,CWigan
OL,7,FIan Crewe, Area Director for Greater
OL,8,FManchester, Merseyside and Cheshire at
OL,9,Fthe Environment Agency, said: "The
OL,10,Fillegal dumping at sites across
OL,11,FEngland are an attack on our
OL,12,Fcommunities, and the Environment
OL,13,FAgency shares their disgust at these
OL,14,Fhorrendous crimes.
OL,16,F"Our teams have been working
OL,17,Frelentlessly on this investigation,
OL,18,Fand yesterday's arrest are a vital
OL,19,Fstep in collecting new evidence and
OL,20,Fprogressing it further."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779369077
OL,3,CMan arrested following investigation
OL,4,Cinto 25-tonne illegal waste dump in
OL,5,CWigan
OL,7,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are cracking down on waste
OL,9,Fcriminals - putting an end to the
OL,10,Fdamage they cause, by boosting funds
OL,11,Fto tackle waste crime, putting more
OL,12,Fboots on the ground and and giving
OL,13,Fstronger powers to our enforcement
OL,14,Fteams.
OL,16,F"If you dump waste illegally, we will
OL,17,Fcome after you."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
